        "large_text": "Challenge Details and Information: ",
        "small_text": "<p>The Get Organized Challenge is a series of 8 classes. Challenge classes are <strong>FREE<\/strong>. You don't need any particular tools or equipment to participate. My goal is to help you establish good organizational systems and strategies. Each week we'll talk about one major category or idea. The week following the Challenge class you'll spend as much time as possible completing the Challenge homework. I hope you'll sign up to join us! We get a lot done AND have fun, too.<\/p>",
